data.description: Welcome to 4783 Bayshore Dr. Get ready to call this place home! 3 bedrooms, 1.75 bathrooms, 1536 sf, built in 1999. Great neighborhood close to all of the Birch Bay and Blaine amenities. Big, level backyard is fully fenced and has a patio, fruit trees, garden space, storage shed, and firepit. Attached 2 car garage with built-in shelving. This house offers a nice layout/floor plan with efficient gas forced air heat including a gas fireplace in the living area.
